    "en": {
      "title": "Thirteen arrested for attacking filling station in Wellawaya",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The police have arrested 13 people in total for their unruly behaviour at a filling station in Wellawaya town.",
        "According to the police, the suspects had hurled stones and bottles at the filling station after it was announced that the pumps have run dry.",
        "A tense situation had ensued as the people who queued up outside the filling station to obtain fuel began to display disorderly conduct.",
        "Reportedly, one police officer who was on duty\u00a0sustained injuries in the incident, while the signboard of the filling station was damaged.",
        "The arrestees were identified as residents of Passara, Ethiliweya and Wellawaya areas, aged between 18 and 45 years.",
        "The police also took 20 motorcycles into custody, along with the 13 suspects.",
        "They will be produced before Wellawaya Magistrate\u2019s Court later today (July 06)."
      ],
